# MIRAKL CONNECT ‚Äî Design System & Rules

## Brand Identity
- Name: **MIRAKL CONNECT**
- Sub-label: **Operations**
- Font stack: **Roboto Serif** (headings, body, labels, cards), **JetBrains Mono** (data, monospace values)

## Color Palette

### Primary
- `primary`: #004bd9
- `primary-container`: #2764ff (buttons, active states, accents)
- `on-primary`: #ffffff

### Secondary / Urgent
- `secondary`: #b70051
- `urgent`: #F22E75
- `urgent-soft`: #FFE7EC
- `error`: #ba1a1a

### Surfaces
- `background`: #F2F8FF (page background)
- `surface`: #faf8ff
- `surface-raised`: #FFFFFF (cards, panels)
- `surface-container`: #ededfa
- `surface-container-low`: #f3f2ff
- `surface-container-high`: #e7e7f4

### Text
- `on-surface`: #191b24 (primary text)
- `on-background`: #191b24
- `ink`: #03182F (dark elements like chat bar)
- `foreground-muted`: #30373E
- `foreground-subtle`: #6B7480

### Borders
- `border`: #DDE5EE (default borders)
- `border-strong`: #BFCBDA (emphasized borders)
- `outline`: #737687
- `outline-variant`: #c3c5d8

### Status
- `ok`: #3FA46A (success, fulfilled)
- `warn`: #E0A93A (warning)
- `error`: #ba1a1a (error)
- `urgent`: #F22E75 (risk, critical)

## Border Radius
- Default: `0.125rem` (2px) ‚Äî sharp, editorial feel
- `rounded-lg`: `0.25rem` (4px)
- `rounded-xl`: `0.5rem` (8px)
- `rounded-full`: `0.75rem` (12px) ‚Äî pills, badges
- Exception: chat bar uses `rounded-full` (fully round)

## Typography Classes
- `font-h1` / `font-h2`: Roboto Serif, bold, tracking-tight
- `font-body`: Roboto Serif, regular
- `font-label-caps`: Roboto Serif, uppercase, small, tracking-wide ‚Äî used for section labels
- `font-card-title`: Roboto Serif, medium weight
- `font-caption`: Roboto Serif, small, subtle color
- `font-kpi-value`: Roboto Serif, large/bold ‚Äî KPI numbers
- `font-mono-data`: JetBrains Mono ‚Äî order IDs, timestamps, data values

## Component Patterns

### Sidebar (SideNavBar)
- Fixed left, `w-60`, white background, `border-r border-slate-100`
- Logo: "MIRAKL CONNECT" in `text-xl font-black tracking-widest`
- Sub-label: uppercase, `text-xs text-slate-400`
- Nav items: `mx-2 px-3 py-2`, flex with icon + label
- Active: `bg-slate-50 text-primary-container border border-slate-200 rounded-md`
- Inactive: `text-slate-500`, hover ‚Üí `bg-slate-50 text-slate-900`
- Icons: Material Symbols Outlined, weight 300, size 20px

### Top Bar
- `h-14`, white, `border-b border-slate-100`, sticky top
- Brand name left, user info + avatar right

### Cards
- `bg-surface-raised border border-border p-6`
- No shadow by default ‚Äî rely on border
- Section label: uppercase `font-label-caps text-foreground-subtle`
- KPI value: `font-kpi-value text-on-surface` (large)
- Delta/change: `text-ok italic text-sm` or colored accordingly

### Tables
- Container: `bg-surface-raised border border-border`
- Header row: `bg-surface-container-low`, uppercase labels
- Cells: `px-6 py-4`
- Row hover: `hover:bg-surface-container-lowest`
- Status badges: `px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full text-[11px] font-bold`
  - Fulfilled: `text-ok bg-ok/10`
  - Processing: `text-primary-container bg-primary-container/10`
  - Risk: `text-urgent bg-urgent-soft`

### Decision Cards
- Same card pattern with colored label (urgent or primary)
- Icon top-right matching label color
- Two buttons: primary (`bg-primary-container text-white`) + secondary (`border border-border-strong`)

### AI Chat Bar
- `bg-ink rounded-full py-3 px-6`
- Dark bar, white text, subtle border `border-white/10`
- Icon: `text-primary-container`
- Submit button: `bg-primary-container text-white rounded-full`

### Status Badges
- Pill shape: `rounded-full px-2 py-0.5 text-[11px] font-bold font-serif`
- Colors match status (ok, primary, urgent, warn)

## Layout Rules
- Max content width: `max-w-[1440px] mx-auto`
- Page padding: `p-6`
- Grid gaps: `gap-6`
- Section spacing: `space-y-6`
- Sidebar width: `w-60` (240px), main content: `ml-60`

## Interaction Patterns
- Hover transitions: `transition-all duration-200 ease-in-out`
- Focus rings: `focus-within:ring-2 focus-within:ring-primary-container/20`
- Button hover: darken or `hover:bg-slate-50`

## General Rules
- Use Roboto Serif everywhere except data/mono values
- Keep the editorial, clean, serif-first aesthetic
- Borders over shadows ‚Äî flat design with subtle depth
- Status colors are semantic: green=ok, blue=info, pink/red=urgent
- Uppercase labels for section headers with wide tracking
- Material Symbols Outlined for all icons (weight 300)
